          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1635848002738-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a separate baking tray with <strong>non-stick baking paper </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Wrap the <strong>browned meat-free sausages </strong>in the<strong> blankets </strong>and add them to the tray – these are your <strong>plant-based</strong> <strong>pigs in blankets</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven, along with the tray of spring greens, for 15 min or until the sliced spring greens are tender and the plant-based pigs in blankets are golden and cooked through</p>",
      "order": 5,
